---
title: Crumbed Chicken Nuggets with Potato Fries & Charred Corn Salad
description: Our recipe developer, Paddy says "Relax!", because with his easy recipe for chicken nuggets up your sleeve you can take the stress out of dinnertime. Sweet mustard spice gives lots of flavour to the chicken, while potato fries and a tasty charred corn salad round out this simple crowd-pleaser.
